{"tid":1410942,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［重要］集會一定要如期舉行","createTime":"2019-08-05T02:41:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T04:04:11.000Z","uid":34086,"like":73,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"a5ffbbed4b74be49f7930144224063a7070c9028","tid":1410942,"uid":34086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T02:41:53.000Z","msg":"見到幾個塞交通post都話要改時間到夜晚先開始集會，等班「罷唔到工」嘅市民可以有藉口全日唔返工<br />\n<br />\n呢啲主意完全係痴撚線！<br />\n<br />\n集會講明一點開始，就應該要晏晝通返車俾各兄弟出發集會<br />\n<br />\n嗰啲唔想嘥AL又唔想SL嘅人，想unun腳要手足幫你地塞鐵<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔該你地咪撚再咁自私啦</span></span><br />\n<br />\n出面班手足幫你擋彈 幫你衝 幫你俾人拉<br />\n你地請個假都唔撚肯 仲想搞亂個集會時間<br />\n<br />\n想坐享其成？你地唔撚配呀！<br />\n<br />\n一點集會！一定要準時！！！"},{"pid":"1b5c03cf5994e9bcb6b649b3ae9258cdd6e877c0","tid":1410942,"uid":34086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T02:44:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bb7b9d522a2c31d3c3aa8acc9a3b40f769d0603a","tid":1410942,"uid":4496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T02:44:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9d64e975bc03c0e56d4ea65665ddd41906dc3d9a","tid":1410942,"uid":34086,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T02:45:22.000Z","msg":"絕對唔係分化緊<br />\n分化係指兄分爬山 各有各做<br />\n唔係你地班喺屋企坐緊 乜都唔做"},{"pid":"47de8b9426579e9d6bce3f3733323d066eaaa261","tid":1410942,"uid":34086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T02:45:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3777a860d653277eebb4df5fb8f9e2f89afeafc6","tid":1410942,"uid":34086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T02:45:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c45f7cf78b99dfa816fe01b5e38c588a508f4ee3","tid":1410942,"uid":266289,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T02:46:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rrH6ADn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrrH6ADn.png&h=385dceac&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZT2V